params.description: - Create customer-receptionist email chats where the customer is requesting to book a venue for a party reservation.

rows.subject: Venue Booking Inquiry
rows.body: Hi, I'd like to book your venue for a birthday party on June 20th. Is that date available?

rows.subject: Re: Venue Booking Inquiry
rows.body: Hello Jane, June 20th is available. How many guests do you expect?

rows.subject: Party Venue Reservation Request
rows.body: Hi, I am interested in reserving the banquet hall for a graduation party on July 12th. Please let me know the process.

rows.subject: Re: Party Venue Reservation Request
rows.body: Hi Matthew, Thank you for your interest. The banquet hall is available on July 12th. Would you like to schedule a tour?

rows.subject: Booking Inquiry for Anniversary Party
rows.body: Hello, I want to book a space for our anniversary party on August 15th. Can you provide pricing details?

rows.subject: Re: Booking Inquiry for Anniversary Party
rows.body: Hi Linda, Congratulations! Our packages start at $500. Would you like to see the full menu and amenities?

rows.subject: Reservation for Kids Party
rows.body: Good afternoon, Is your venue available for a children's party on September 10th?

rows.subject: Re: Reservation for Kids Party
rows.body: Hello Alex, September 10th is open. How many kids are you expecting? Any special requirements?

rows.subject: Venue Availability for Baby Shower
rows.body: Hi, I am planning a baby shower on May 25th. Is your event hall free on that date?

rows.subject: Re: Venue Availability for Baby Shower
rows.body: Hi Emma, Yes, May 25th is available for your baby shower. Let us know your preferred time.

rows.subject: Request to Book Venue for Engagement
rows.body: Hello, I'd like to reserve your venue for an engagement party on July 5th. Please advise on next steps.

rows.subject: Re: Request to Book Venue for Engagement
rows.body: Hi Paul, July 5th is open. We can hold the date for you. Would you like catering options?

rows.subject: Party Space Reservation Needed
rows.body: Hi, Is your party space available for a reunion on June 30th?

rows.subject: Re: Party Space Reservation Needed
rows.body: Hi Nina, June 30th is currently free. How many guests are you planning for?

rows.subject: Booking Request for Sweet 16
rows.body: Hello, I wish to book your event hall for my daughter's sweet 16 on August 2nd. Please confirm availability.

rows.subject: Re: Booking Request for Sweet 16
rows.body: Hi Carla, August 2nd is available for your event. Would you like to discuss decoration options?

rows.subject: Reserve Venue for Company Party
rows.body: Good morning, I'd like to reserve your venue for a company party on July 19th. Please let me know the deposit.

rows.subject: Re: Reserve Venue for Company Party
rows.body: Hello Oliver, July 19th is open. The deposit is $200. Shall I send the payment link?

rows.subject: Venue Booking for Surprise Party
rows.body: Hi, I want to book your venue for a surprise party on June 10th. Is it possible?

rows.subject: Re: Venue Booking for Surprise Party
rows.body: Hi Sophie, June 10th is free for booking. Let us know your requirements.
